{"tid":826410,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"開拍新版《還珠格格》 瓊瑤：以年輕人喜歡方式翻拍","createTime":"2018-09-18T08:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T09:56:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"20ef4868169c9b5b58ce7156d5c277e35a2cff29","tid":826410,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RG54iQIGv3vPXX9Ti2GGcQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180918f123322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRG54iQIGv3vPXX9Ti2GGcQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180918f123322.jpg&h=214c3258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】台灣小說作家兼編劇瓊瑤昨日宣布將開拍新版《還珠格格》，瓊瑤透露，翻拍重點將會從年輕人喜歡的方式出發，用全新的方式講述經典故事。<br />\n<br />\n1998年播出的清宮劇經典《還珠格格》紅了20年仍曆久不衰，內地甚至每年暑假皆會重播。劇集的編劇瓊瑤近日公開證實，將重新編制這部經典劇，同時開發相關的動漫和遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n而網民對於翻指《還珠》的反應好壞參半，有人指期待新版本，但亦有不少人擔心新版或會破壞舊版的經典，又指會有損他們的童年回憶。"},{"pid":"4a1fee07703bd75e69c60a01b9559aa701fce373","tid":826410,"uid":52590,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又黎<br />\n上套除左 趙麗穎之後仲有冇人紅到"},{"pid":"a1710fac5c3d127f85b695b4abbf02e0024cd181","tid":826410,"uid":37876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:30:37.000Z","msg":"之前咪拍過囉唔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1e78fe222f1358b556d1c4fdca96a3cd5d3bb5","tid":826410,"uid":39365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:32:00.000Z","msg":"好似流星花園咁不斷翻拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a957b5b407b6f23a21af4cc3bf8c61cc56ebdbcf","tid":826410,"uid":22999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a1fee07703bd75e69c60a